import React from "react"
import ReactDOM from "react-dom"
import {BrowserRouter as Router} from "react-router-dom"

import {ContextProvider} from "./cartcontext";
import App from "./App"

ReactDOM.render(
    <ContextProvider>
    <Router>
        <App />
    </Router>
    </ContextProvider>,
    document.getElementById("root")
)
